{
  "chapter": "029",
  "title": "河渠书",
  "translations": {
    "1": {
      "title": "禹治黄河开创水利之功",
      "text": "<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">夏书</span>说：<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">禹</span>抑制洪水<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">十三年（时长）</span>，路过家门都不进入。陆路行走乘坐<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">车</span>，水路行走乘坐<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">舟</span>，泥地行走脚踏<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">毳</span>板，山路行走就乘<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">桥</span>檋。以此区分<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">九州</span>，沿着山势疏浚河川，依照土地肥瘠制定贡赋。开通<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">九</span>条道路，修筑<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">九</span>个湖泽的堤防，测量<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">九</span>座山岭。然而<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">黄河</span>泛滥横溢，对<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">中国</span>危害尤其严重。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">禹</span>专以治河为要务。旧<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">故道</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">黄河</span>从<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">积石</span>经过<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">龙门</span>，南到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">华阴</span>，东下<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">砥柱</span>，到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">孟津</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">洛汭</span>，直至<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">大邳</span>。于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">禹</span>认为<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">黄河</span>所来之处地势太高，水流湍急凶悍，难以在平地上行走，屡次造成溃决，就分出<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二</span>条渠道来引导<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">黄河</span>。向北承引到高地，经过<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">降水</span>，到达<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">大陆</span>泽，分播为<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">九河</span>，再合为<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">逆河</span>，流入<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">勃海</span>。<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">九</span>条河川已经疏通，<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">九</span>个湖泽已经排水，<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">诸夏</span>得以安定，功业施及<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">三代</span>。"
    },
    "2": {
      "title": "战国至秦代诸国水利工程",
      "text": "此后，从<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">荥阳</span>以下引<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">黄河</span>东南流而成为<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">鸿沟</span>，用以通连<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">宋</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">郑</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">陈</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">蔡</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">曹</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">卫</span>，与<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">济水</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">汝</span>水、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">淮河</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">泗水</span>相会。在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>国，西方则开渠通连<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">汉水</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">云梦之野</span>，东方则开渠通连<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">江淮</span>之间。在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>国，则开渠通连<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">三江</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">五湖</span>。在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>国，则开渠通连<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">菑</span>水、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">济水</span>之间。在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">蜀</span>，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">蜀守</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李冰\">冰（李冰）</span>凿开<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">离碓</span>，避免<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">沫水</span>的危害，在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">成都</span>城中开凿<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二</span>江。这些渠道都可以通行<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">舟</span>船，多余的水还可用来灌溉田地，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">百姓</span>享受其利益。至于渠水经过的地方，常常引水加以灌溉田畴的小渠，以<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">万亿</span>计，无法尽数。"
    },
    "3": {
      "title": "西门豹引漳溉邺",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">西门豹</span>引<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">漳水</span>灌溉<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">鄴</span>地，以使<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>国的<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">河内</span>富饶。"
    },
    "4": {
      "title": "郑国渠建成使秦富强",
      "text": "而<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>听说<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国喜好兴办工程，想使秦国疲敝，不让它东进攻伐，就派<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">水工</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">郑国</span>作为间谍去游说<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国，让秦国开凿<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">泾水</span>自<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">中山</span>西面起到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">瓠口</span>作为渠道，沿着<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">北山</span>东流注入<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">洛水</span>，绵延<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">三百馀里</span>，想用来灌溉田地。工程中途被察觉，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国想要<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">郑国</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">郑国</span>说：\"当初我作为间谍，然而渠道修成也是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国的利益。\" <span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国认为有理，终究让他修完渠道。渠道修成，引含有淤泥的水灌溉盐碱地<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">四万馀顷</span>，收成都是每亩<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">一钟</span>。于是<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">关中</span>成为沃野，没有荒年，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国因此富强，最终兼并<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>，因此命名这条渠道为<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">郑国渠</span>。"
    },
    "5": {
      "title": "汉文帝时黄河决酸枣",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>朝兴起<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">三十九年（时长）</span>时，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孝文</span>时<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">黄河</span>在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">酸枣</span>决口，向东冲溃<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">金隄</span>，于是<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">东郡</span>大规模征发<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">卒</span>兵堵塞决口。"
    },
    "6": {
      "title": "汉武帝初期河决瓠子未能塞",
      "text": "此后<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">四十多年（时长）</span>，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">今天子</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：年号\">元光（年号）</span>年间，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">黄河</span>在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">瓠子</span>决口，向东南注入<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">钜野</span>泽，通连<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">淮河</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">泗水</span>。于是<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">汲黯</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">郑当时</span>征调人徒堵塞决口，堵好就又坏。这时<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">武安侯</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田蚡</span>任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span>，他的食邑在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">鄃</span>。<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">鄃</span>地位于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">黄河</span>北，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">黄河</span>决口向南泄，则<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">鄃</span>就没有水灾，食邑收入就多。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：田蚡\">蚡（田蚡）</span>对皇上说：\"<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">长江</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">黄河</span>决口都是天意，不容易用人力强行堵塞，堵塞未必合乎天意。\" 而<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">望气</span>占卜的人也认为如此。于是<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>很久都不再从事堵塞决口之事。"
    },
    "7": {
      "title": "郑当时建议开凿漕渠",
      "text": "这时<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">郑当时</span>任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">大农</span>，说：\"从前<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">关东</span>漕运粟米要从<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">渭水</span>溯流而上，需要<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">六月（时长）</span>才能罢，而漕运的水道长<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">九百馀里</span>，时常有难以通行之处。引<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">渭水</span>开凿渠道起于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">长安</span>，沿着<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">南山</span>下，到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">黄河</span>共<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">三百馀里</span>，路径径直，容易漕运，估计可以让漕运<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">三月（时长）</span>就罢；而渠下民田有<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">万馀</span>顷，又可以灌溉田地：这样既减省漕运节约卒役，又使<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">关中</span>的土地更加肥沃，得到粮食。\" <span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>认为有理，令<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>人<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">水工</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">徐伯</span>勘测标定，全部征发<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">卒</span>兵<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">数万人</span>开凿漕渠，<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">三年（时长）</span>就打通了。通渠后用于漕运，非常便利。其后漕运稍稍增多，而渠下的百姓颇能得到灌溉田地的好处。"
    },
    "8": {
      "title": "河东渠田工程失败",
      "text": "其后<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">河东守</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">番系</span>说：\"漕运从<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">山东</span>往西，每年<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">百馀万石</span>，要经过<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">砥柱</span>的险阻，损失很多，而且又烦劳耗费。开凿渠道引<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">汾</span>水灌溉<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">皮氏</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">汾阴</span>一带，引<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">黄河</span>灌溉<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">汾阴</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">蒲坂</span>一带，估计可得<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">五千</span>顷。这<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">五千</span>顷原来都是<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">黄河</span>边废弃的地，百姓在其中割草放牧，如今若灌溉为田，估计可得粮食<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二百万石</span>以上。粮食从<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">渭水</span>向上运，与<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">关中</span>没有差别，而<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">砥柱</span>以东就可以不再漕运。\" <span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>认为有理，征发<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">卒</span>兵<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">数万人</span>开渠造田。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">数年（时长）</span>，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">黄河</span>迁移，渠道不利，种田的人连种子都收不回。久而久之，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">河东</span>的渠田废弃了，就给予<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">越</span>人，令<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">少府</span>把它作为少量收入。"
    },
    "9": {
      "title": "褒斜道开通但水运不成",
      "text": "其后有人上书想打通<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">襃斜道</span>以便漕运，皇上把事交给<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">御史大夫</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张汤</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张汤\">汤（张汤）</span>询问这件事，于是进言说：\"前往<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">蜀</span>地从<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">故道</span>走，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">故道</span>多山坡，迂回遥远。现在开通<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">襃斜道</span>，山坡少，缩短<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">四百里</span>；而<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">襃水</span>通<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">沔</span>水，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">斜水</span>通<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">渭水</span>，都可以通行<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">船</span>漕运。漕运从<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">南阳</span>上溯<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">沔</span>水进入<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">襃</span>水，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">襃</span>水与<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">斜</span>水之间断水处约<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">百馀里</span>，用<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">车</span>转运，从<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">斜</span>水下至<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">渭水</span>。这样，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">汉中</span>的粮食就可以运达，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">山东</span>的粮食从<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">沔</span>水上运没有限制，比<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">砥柱</span>漕运还便利。而且<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">襃斜</span>一带<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">材木</span><span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">竹箭</span>的丰饶，可比<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">巴蜀</span>。\" <span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>认为有理，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">拜</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张汤\">汤（张汤）</span>的儿子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张卬\">卬（张卬）</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">汉中守</span>，征发<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">数万人</span>修建<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">襃斜道</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">五百馀里</span>。道路果然便捷，但水流湍急多石，无法漕运。"
    },
    "10": {
      "title": "龙首渠开凿工程",
      "text": "其后<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">庄熊罴</span>上言：\"<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">临晋</span>的百姓希望开凿<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">洛水</span>以灌溉<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">重泉</span>以东<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">万馀</span>顷的盐碱地。如果真能引水，可以每亩收<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">十石</span>。\" 于是征发<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">卒</span>兵<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">万馀人</span>开凿渠道，从<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">徵</span>地引<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">洛水</span>到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">商颜山</span>下。两岸容易崩塌，就开凿<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">井</span>，深的有<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">四十馀</span>丈。一个接一个地打<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">井</span>，<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">井</span>下相通以引水流通。水从<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">商颜</span>山下暗流而过，东到山岭间<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">十馀里</span>。<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">井渠</span>的做法由此开始。开凿渠道时挖出龙骨，所以命名为<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">龙首渠</span>。工程进行了<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">十多年（时长）</span>，渠道略通，但还未得到充分效益。"
    },
    "11": {
      "title": "武帝亲临决河成功堵塞瓠子",
      "text": "自从<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">黄河</span>在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">瓠子</span>决口后<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">二十多年（时长）</span>，收成因此屡年不好，而<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>之地尤其严重。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>既已<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">封禅</span>巡祭山川，第二年，干旱，封禅完后少雨。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>于是派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">汲仁</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">郭昌</span>征发<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">卒</span>兵<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">数万人</span>堵塞<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">瓠子</span>决口。于是<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">万里沙</span>祭祀完毕，回程就亲临决河之处，把<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">白马</span><span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">玉璧</span>沉入<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">黄河</span>中，令<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">群臣</span>随从官员从<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将军</span>以下都背负<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">薪</span>柴填塞决口。这时<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">东郡</span>的野<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">草</span>被烧光，因此<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">薪</span>柴稀少，于是砍伐<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">淇园</span>的<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">竹</span>子来作为<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">楗</span>桩。"
    },
    "12": {
      "title": "武帝作歌悼治河之艰",
      "text": "<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>既然亲临<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">黄河</span>决口，悲伤功业未成，就作歌道：\"<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">瓠子</span>决口啊将怎么办？浩浩荡荡啊乡闾都化为<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">黄河</span>川！都化为<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">黄河</span>川啊地无宁日，功业无止时啊吾山被削平。吾山被削平啊<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">钜野</span>泽水溢出，<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">鱼</span>群沸腾啊已近冬日。延伸的河道松弛啊偏离常流，<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">蛟龙</span>驰骋啊远游四方。归于旧道啊神哉盛大，不行<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">封禅</span>啊怎知外患！替我告诉<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">河伯</span>啊为何不仁，泛滥不止啊令我百姓忧愁？<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">齧桑</span>浮在水上啊<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">淮河</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">泗水</span>满溢，久不回归啊水道缓滞。\" 又一首：“<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">黄河</span>汤汤啊激流潺湲，北渡浑浊啊浚流艰难。拿起长竹索啊沉下美<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">玉</span>，<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">河伯</span>答应了啊<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">薪</span>柴不继。<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">薪</span>柴不继啊是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">卫</span>人的过错，野火烧尽啊唉呀用什么抵御水！林<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">竹</span>倒下啊<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">楗</span>桩插立，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">宣房</span>堵塞啊万福来临。\" 于是终于堵塞了<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">瓠子</span>决口，在其上筑起<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">宫</span>室，命名为<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">宣房宫</span>。 又引导<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">黄河</span>向北流行<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二</span>条渠道，恢复<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">禹</span>的旧迹，于是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>之地重新安宁，没有水灾。"
    },
    "13": {
      "title": "各地水利工程大兴",
      "text": "从此以后，主事之人争相倡言水利。<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">朔方</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">西河</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">河西</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">酒泉</span>都引<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">黄河</span>及川谷水以灌溉田地；<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">关中</span>的辅渠、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">灵轵</span>渠引<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">堵水</span>；<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">汝南</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">九江</span>引<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">淮河</span>；<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">东海</span>引<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">钜定</span>；<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">泰山</span>下引<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">汶水</span>：都开凿渠道为灌溉田地，各<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">万馀</span>顷。其他小渠辟山通道的，不可胜言。然而其中最著名的还是<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">宣房</span>。"
    },
    "14": {
      "title": "太史公游历总结作河渠书",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太史公</span>说：我南登<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">庐山</span>，观察<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">禹</span>疏浚<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">九江</span>的遗迹，于是到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">会稽</span>的<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">太湟</span>，登<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">姑苏</span>山，远望<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">五湖</span>；东观<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">洛汭</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">大邳</span>，迎视<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">黄河</span>，沿行<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">淮河</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">泗水</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">济水</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">漯洛渠</span>；西望<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">蜀</span>地的<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">岷山</span>和<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">离碓</span>；北从<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">龙门</span>到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">朔方</span>。感叹说：水对百姓的利害真是太大了啊！我从跟随众人背负<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">薪</span>柴堵塞<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">宣房</span>决口，悲叹<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">瓠子</span>之诗，因而撰作<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">河渠书</span>。"
    },
    "15": {
      "title": "全篇总赞",
      "text": "水的利害，自古以来就是如此。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">禹</span>疏浚沟洫，随山势浚通河川。 直到后世，并非没有<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">圣贤</span>。 <span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">鸿沟</span>开划之后，又穿凿得龙骨的渠道。 淤泥填积得以耕种，黎民百姓有了丰年。 <span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">宣房</span>受到歌咏，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>之地得以保全。"
    }
  }
